## 🛡️ FORBIDDEN OPERATIONS

### Schema Changes
- **NEVER** rename amount, debit_account_id, or credit_account_id columns
- **NEVER** suggest new roles without explicit approval
- **NEVER** create duplicate tables with different names
- **NEVER** modify existing tables without migration scripts

### Role Modifications
- **NEVER** change grids@microtronic.biz role from superadmin
- **NEVER** create SUPER_ADMIN role in any form
- **NEVER** suggest role hierarchy changes
- **ALWAYS** verify roles against CORE_RULES.md

### Code Suggestions
- **NEVER** suggest fixes for "missing columns" without schema verification
- **NEVER** propose table structures without referencing trusted sources
- **NEVER** create conflicting documentation
- **ALWAYS** verify existing code before suggesting changes

---

## 🔍 VERIFICATION CHECKLIST

### Before Any Schema Change
- [ ] Checked CORE_RULES.md for current schema
- [ ] Verified existing table structure with SQL
- [ ] Confirmed column names match documentation
- [ ] Referenced add-table-comments.sql for purposes
- [ ] Ensured no role conflicts with owner identity

### Before Any Role Change
- [ ] Confirmed grids@microtronic.biz remains superadmin
- [ ] Checked for SUPER_ADMIN references to remove
- [ ] Verified role definitions match CORE_RULES.md
- [ ] Ensured no conflicting role permissions

### Before Any Code Change
- [ ] Verified database schema matches expectations
- [ ] Checked for "missing column" errors in logs
- [ ] Confirmed table purposes are understood
- [ ] Referenced trusted sources for guidance

